[ # Usability is where you are allowed to use something.
Something with a build usability can be used in any of the
other on-[ build, run, test ]. Something with a usability of
run can be used in run and test. Something with test can
only be used in test.

By default definitions are marked with run. ]
[ union
    [ Usable
        [ build ]
        [ run ]
        [ test ]

        [ usable build ]
        [ visibility public ]
    ]

]